all books in the bible are infallible - literally the same as original, ideological the same as original, theological the same as original.&nbsp;<div><br></div><div><br><div><br></div><div>But not all books are equally important for sinful persons. A person can be a Christian without reading all books.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>All books are different in literature and they can be classified in to different categories.&nbsp;<br><div><br></div><div>They have hierarchy priority orders for sinful readers. Some of the books must read first and accept. Some books are personal favorite after believe. Some books are the testifying or verification of the believers in their life and must read later.&nbsp;<br><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div></div></div></div>